summary: Defines the OutlinedButton control, a medium‑emphasis button widget that can display text and/or an icon, be enabled or disabled, handle user interaction events (click, hover, focus, long‑press), navigate to URLs, and be styled through various visual properties.
business_intent: Offers developers a pre‑built, customizable button component for rapid UI development within the Flet framework, simplifying event handling, navigation, and visual consistency across applications.
